[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/169loqo.png[/img] Hello fellow mopar users, [b]i know i am a first time poster but that [u]DOES NOT[/u] mean i'm new![/b] I have been working with 508+ for about a year now and i think it's time i work on a development team. I currently am hosting a domain and i want to compete with the other 667/704+'s out there. Here is a list of all the positions;
Web Developer [1/2]; Krypt,
Client/Cache sided development [0/2]
Server sided Development [2/4]; Krypt, Zingerman111
GFX artist (photoshop+ required) [0/2]
Video producer (camtasia+ required) [0/2]
[b]All applications must be this format;[/b]
Name, Age, Experience, How long have you been developing, (3 months req.) Why you deserve position,
[b]I will message you via moparscape if you are accepted ;)[/b]
